OL,7,FHe added: "The designation process in
OL,8,FGalloway has been less than
OL,9,Fsatisfactory.
OL,11,F"There have been significant issues,
OL,12,Fincluding a perceived bias and a lack
OL,13,Fof any detail on how a Galloway
OL,14,Fnational park would or could be
OL,15,Fdifferent from the two existing
OL,16,Fnational parks, given the area's
OL,17,Fhugely important dairy farming,
OL,18,Fforestry and renewables sectors. That
OL,19,Fhas resulted in mistrust and divisions
OL,20,Fwithin communities, which will take
OL,21,Fyears to heal."
