OL,7,FIn response Gillian Martin, the Acting
OL,8,FCabinet Secretary for Net Zero and
OL,9,FEnergy said: "As Mr Carson knows,
OL,10,Fthere was a thorough and comprehensive
OL,11,Fconsultation process`5,000
OL,12,Fconsultation surveys were completed
OL,13,Fand more than 30 consultation events
OL,14,Fwere held across the area covered by
OL,15,Fthe proposals, with more than 1,000
OL,16,Fpeople attending.
