OL,7,F"The rural affairs secretary has to
OL,8,Flook at the results of the
OL,9,Fconsultation and take them seriously.
OL,10,FAn awful lot of information is
OL,11,Fincluded in the consultation, and she
OL,12,Fwill advise the Parliament when she is
OL,13,Fready to do so."
OL,15,FITV News Border's Scottish Political
OL,16,FEditor, Kieran Andrews, said three
OL,17,Fwell placed sources he'd spoken to
OL,18,Fsuggested the consultation threw
OL,19,F"serious doubt over whether the plans
OL,20,Fcan go ahead."
