OL,7,FSources told Andrews that when it came
OL,8,Fto people in favour, and against, the
OL,9,Fplans in the consultation the numbers
OL,10,Fwere "close."
OL,12,FBut he added: "The fact support is not
OL,13,Foverwhelming is a big blow to the
OL,14,Fplans."
OL,16,FScottish Government Ministers will
OL,17,Fultimately make the decision on
OL,18,Fwhether to confirm Galloway as the
OL,19,Fsite for a new National Park.
