OL,7,FWhat is the Galloway National Park
OL,8,Fproposal?
OL,10,FLast summer Galloway was selected as
OL,11,Fthe proposed site for a new National
OL,12,FPark by Scottish Government Ministers.
OL,14,FNature Scot then launched a
OL,15,Fconsultation speaking to local people
OL,16,Fand businesses about the proposals.
OL,17,FThe report has now been presented to
OL,18,FGovernment Ministers - but it's not
OL,19,Fyet been released to the public.
