OL,7,FThey have become incredibly
OL,8,Fcontroversial, with a 'No Galloway
OL,9,FNational Park' group set up to oppose
OL,10,Fthe plans. The group has since held
OL,11,Fprotests and attracted thousands of
OL,12,Ffollowers on social media.
OL,14,FIn February, Dumfries and Galloway
OL,15,FCouncil said it was 'undecided' on
OL,16,Fwhether the plans should go ahead.
